issue.title: User format email
issue.body:
The User model jsonSchema validation to format email throws an error
```
Error: unknown format "email" ignored in schema at path "#/properties/email" at unknownFormat
```

Has been resolved by using regex `pattern` instead
```
// models/User.js

...
properties: {
        email: { type: "string", pattern: "^\\S+@\\S+\\.\\S+$" },
...
```
